data.description: GREAT FISHING AND HUNTING PROPERTY! NO COVENANTS! Imagine 6.43 acres overlooking Blue Mesa Lake and the Dillon Pinnacles! Ample room for your RV and outdoor toys. Ideally located between Gunnison and Montrose, off of Hwy 50. This unique property can be a comfortable home or an excellent fishing and hunting lodge. The 3-bedroom, 2 bath log home features a spacious, open family/living/dining/kitchen area! Fantastic boating, fishing, and hunting near by! Here's your chance to enjoy Blue Mesa Lake and the surrounding area. A great opportunity for a home-based hunting and fishing business.
